## Definition of done

### Rust toolchain
- [ ] `rustup show` confirms stable toolchain is active
- [ ] Rust version is ≥ {{rust_version}}: `rustc --version`
- [ ] Nightly toolchain installed (required for `cargo-fuzz`): `rustup install nightly`

### Required tools
- [ ] `cargo audit` installed and working: `cargo audit --version`
- [ ] `cargo deny` installed and working: `cargo deny --version`
- [ ] `cargo geiger` installed and working: `cargo geiger --version`
- [ ] `cargo semver-checks` installed: `cargo semver-checks --version`
- [ ] `cargo fuzz` installed (nightly): `cargo +nightly fuzz --version`

### Repository
- [ ] Repository cloned via SSH (not HTTPS)
- [ ] `git remote -v` shows the correct remote URL
- [ ] On the correct branch (usually `main`)

### Build and tests
- [ ] `cargo build` succeeds with no errors
- [ ] `cargo test` passes with all tests green
- [ ] `cargo clippy -- -D warnings` passes

### Plugin tools (if applicable)
- [ ] `.claude/plugins/` built: `cd .claude/plugins && cargo build --release`

### Security baseline
- [ ] `cargo audit` run — findings reviewed (not necessarily zero)
- [ ] `cargo deny check` run — findings reviewed

### Editor
- [ ] `rust-analyzer` LSP working in the editor
- [ ] Code completion and diagnostics functioning

